Story

Yoko Nakajima was a girl who had pretended the honor student in the school and also in the home. One day, a man named Keiki showed up suddenly, and Yoko was called "Lord" by him. Her destiny began to move greatly from that time.

She was led by Keiki, and the place she had reached at last was an another world where twelve kingdoms existed. Moreover, she lost sight of Keiki, and didn&#039;t know where even to go. An innumerable specter has obstinately attacked such Yoko. Furthermore, she received harsh treatment from the people whom she met. Through the survival in the another world, she regains "Strength to live" which human originally has.

The fantasy novel which is popular with the girls is animated. How does Yoko endure the severe trial imposed on her?
